In fastparquet, there is a flag
export=“hive”, which makes compatible with parquet-mr reader. As a workaround, using fastparquet,
although keeping pyarrow would be better.

Actually the regex is 
{noformat}
"(.+) version ((.*) )?\\(build ?(.*)\\)";
{noformat}
so we would need "parquet-cpp-arrow version 6.0.0 (build SNAPSHOT)"
